---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Complete Guide to Beauty & Cosmetics E-Commerce Marketing in Canada | Lead Flow North">
  <article class="py-12 md:py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <!-- Back Link -->
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-8">
        <a href="/industries/ecommerce-retail/beauty-cosmetics" class="inline-flex items-center text-sky-600 hover:text-sky-700 dark:text-sky-300 font-medium">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path></svg>
          Back to Beauty & Cosmetics
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <header class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <span class="bg-pink-100 text-pink-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Beauty & Cosmetics</span>
          <span class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm">14 min read</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
          The Complete Guide to Beauty & Cosmetics Marketing Automation
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 mb-8">
          Build VIP loyalty, drive routine adherence, and create personalized skincare journeys that convert browsers into loyal customers.
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
          
          <p class="lead text-xl text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 mb-8">
            Beauty customers have endless choices. The brands that win are those that create personalized experiences, build routines, and make customers feel like VIPs.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">Personalized Skincare Journeys</h2>

          <p>
            Generic product recommendations don't work in beauty. Skin type quizzes and concern-based segmentation let you deliver truly personalized routines that address individual needs.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">VIP Loyalty Programs</h2>

          <p>
            Your best customers drive most of your revenue. Tiered VIP programs with early access, birthday perks, and exclusive gifts keep them engaged and spending more.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">Routine Building</h2>

          <p>
            Products sitting unused don't get reordered. Education sequences that teach proper application and routine adherence drive usage, results, and repeat purchases.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-600 to-rose-600 p-8 rounded-xl text-white my-12">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Ready to Grow Your Brand?</h3>
            <p class="text-pink-100 mb-6">
              Get a free consultation and see exactly how we'd implement these automations for your beauty brand.
            </p>
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center bg-white text-pink-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-slate-100 transition">
              Book Your Free Demo
            </a>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
